            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "I reread it, the `nil` check should already prevent mixed `/` and `\\` cases. Comparing the whole path might make it clearer that this is the exact exe we expect, rather than sth affected by the `cwd` or other factors? This will probably be useful in #36818. :)",
